hopla set day-start - set the day start (cron) of a user


usage:
    hopla set day-start
    hopla get day-start {N}


> hopla set day-start
set the day start to the default 0 AM

> hopla set day-start {N}
set the day start to the N-th hour. N may range from 0 to 23 (inclusive).


Example:
```bash
# set the the day start to 01:00 AM
$ hopla set day-start 1
```
